com.travelbank.knit

Interface ModelMapInterface


  • public interface ModelMapInterface
    When KnitProcessor scans classpath, it creates a class called ModelMap that implements ModelMapInterface. This class contains all data such as which model requires/generates which data and what their parent classes are. This is how UsageGraph determines dependencies. This class is loaded via KnitUtilsLoader.
